data.description: This conveniently located home offers cozy hospitality and comfort, creating a welcoming space for everyone who steps inside. Inside, the cozy living room flows into the dining room and inviting kitchen. With three bedrooms and two baths, you will have plenty of space for resting and relaxing. Outside, the covered back patio is ideal for entertaining while watching all types of weather unfold. The detached, one-car garage provides shelter and storage for the extras. Do not let this one slip away!
